des: Have the Alexa luxe adventure traveler Skill keep you informed every day with flash briefings, deals of the day, quote of the day, relevant articles, and more. Luxe Adventure Traveler Adventure Travel With a Glass of Wine Travel guides and travel inspiration for soft adventure around the world with a bit of luxury at the end of the day This skill works on all Alexa devices and Alexa enabled smartphones, tablets, and PCs.
